-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Aug 27, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104fjf1665702571973.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fjf1665702571973.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fjf1665702571973.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"fjf1665702571973\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Determines whether Uniface writes a Unicode Byte-Order-Mark (BOM) when the UTF-8 format is specified in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$SYS_CHARSET</span> or with <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">filedump</span> or <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">lfiledump</span>.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"fjf1665702571973__topic_d142022e1_d142023e1_d142024e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fjf1665702571973__p_d142025e1_d142026e1_d142027e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$NO_BOM_UTF8</span> { <code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code> } <code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fjf1665702571973__section_pnd_gfh_jwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d224069e77\">Arguments</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"fjf1665702571973__ul_dyh_hfh_jwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fjf1665702571973__li_d50072e1_d50073e1_d50074e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code>—write a UTF-8 file without a\n               BOM </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fjf1665702571973__li_d50075e1_d50076e1_d50077e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>—write a UTF-8 file with a BOM\n            </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fjf1665702571973__section_q4z_hfh_jwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d224069e96\">Defaults</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"fjf1665702571973__table_d17195e1_d17196e1_d17197e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Assignment file:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Any application assignment file </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Section: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">[SETTINGS] </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default value: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fjf1665702571973__section_vk5_kfh_jwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d224069e144\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fjf1665702571973__p_d142037e1_d142038e1_d142039e1\">When <code class=\"ph codeph\">UTF-8</code> is specified by the\n               <var class=\"keyword varname\">UnicodeFormat</var> parameter with <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">filedump</span> or\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">lfiledump</span>, or the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$SYS_CHARSET</span> assignment\n            setting, Uniface writes a Unicode Byte-Order-Mark (BOM), a special character to\n            recognize the encoding.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fjf1665702571973__p_d142040e1_d142041e1_d142042e1\">However, the generated files may be incompatible\n            with other applications, especially on Unix platforms. To avoid such compatibility\n            issues, you can use the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$NO_BOM_UTF8</span> assignment setting.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bbd1720022831397.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>filedump</a><p>Copy the contents of the source object to the specified file.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qot1665702571691.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>lfiledump</a><p>Copy the contents of the source object to the specified file on the local file system, ignoring file redirections that might occur in the assignment file.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tec1665703247413.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$SYS_CHARSET</a><p>Specify the character set used for communication with the operating system and for communication between Uniface and non-Uniface components, if they are not Unicode-based.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527536\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527536\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$NO_BOM_UTF8 Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 27, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Determines whether Uniface writes a Unicode Byte-Order-Mark (BOM) when the UTF-8 format is specified in $SYS_CHARSET or with filedump or lfiledump . $NO_BOM_UTF8 { = } 1 | 0 Arguments 1 —write a UTF-8 file without a BOM 0 —write a UTF-8 file with a BOM Defaults Assignment file: Any application assignment file Section: [SETTINGS] Default value: 0 Description When UTF-8 is specified by the UnicodeFormat parameter with filedump or lfiledump , or the $SYS_CHARSET assignment setting, Uniface writes a Unicode Byte-Order-Mark (BOM), a special character to recognize the encoding. However, the generated files may be incompatible with other applications, especially on Unix platforms. To avoid such compatibility issues, you can use the $NO_BOM_UTF8 assignment setting. Related Links filedump Copy the contents of the source object to the specified file. lfiledump Copy the contents of the source object to the specified file on the local file system, ignoring file redirections that might occur in the assignment file. $SYS_CHARSET Specify the character set used for communication with the operating system and for communication between Uniface and non-Uniface components, if they are not Unicode-based. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}